label: Supermart Domain
description: Comprehensive example of Domain (pre-joined table sets for complex reporting, custom query based dataset, column and row security, I18n bundles)

queryGroup.name: inventory_fact_1998_2
queryGroup.query: select    i2.product_id as product_id,   i2.time_id as time_id,   i2.warehouse_id as warehouse_id,   i2.store_id as store_id,   i2.units_ordered as units_ordered,   i2.units_shipped as units_shipped,   i2.warehouse_sales as warehouse_sales,   i2.warehouse_cost as warehouse_cost,   i2.supply_time as supply_time,   i2.store_invoice as store_invoice,    (i2.warehouse_sales - i2.warehouse_cost) as warehouse_profit  from   inventory_fact_1998 i2
